can the awakening of the Kundalini or the

00:01:29.940 --> 00:01:37.560
Holy Ghost as described in the Bible can bring
forth this tremendous change; this transformation

00:01:37.560 --> 00:01:50.630
and all the benefits of physical, mental,
emotional and material being within us.

