or in the church or in the temple somewhere;
is all conditioning.

00:23:58.990 --> 00:24:08.509
We do not know for definite whether it is
right or wrong because we haven't got that

00:24:08.509 --> 00:24:09.509
awareness.

00:24:09.509 --> 00:24:18.399
So what has to happen to you is that you have
to become collectively conscious that means

00:24:18.399 --> 00:24:22.059
you can feel your own centers on your finger
tips.

00:24:22.059 --> 00:24:29.960
That is Self-Realization, you know your Self
and you should feel the centers of other people

00:24:29.960 --> 00:24:40.279
on your finger tips and so that you know what
is wrong with another person or what is wrong

00:24:40.279 --> 00:24:41.279
with you.

00:24:41.279 --> 00:24:45.960
But you are so much separated from yourself
like it becomes your cloth, the whole body,

00:24:45.960 --> 00:24:53.629
the ego, the superego that you know it is
wrong and you clear it out, if you know the

00:24:53.629 --> 00:24:54.629
technique.

00:24:54.629 --> 00:24:58.030
This is the another meaning of the word Yoga.

00:24:58.030 --> 00:25:06.320
The first meaning is that Yoga is the union
with the Divine; also Yoga means to be deft

00:25:06.320 --> 00:25:18.220
in the art of God's love, in the technique
of Divine laws; this is the another meaning.

00:25:18.220 --> 00:25:20.600
Yoga doesn't mean standing on your head.

00:25:20.600 --> 00:25:32.169
That's just a misnomer, because some people
have got very little knowledge about things

00:25:32.169 --> 00:25:35.150
and they start saying this is Yoga.

00:25:35.150 --> 00:25:41.049
But I mean Patanjali who has talked about
it thousands of years back has described nothing

00:25:41.049 --> 00:25:49.860
but Sahaja Yoga; is the spontaneous union,
spontaneous union with the Divine.

00:25:49.860 --> 00:25:54.119
That's what he has described out and out but
who reads that big book.

00:25:54.119 --> 00:25:59.490
Yoga you can buy in three pages you see.

00:25:59.490 --> 00:26:06.989
Stand on your head; bend your feet, but why?

00:26:06.989 --> 00:26:13.499
We too have to do some exercises in Sahaja
Yoga but the Kundalini has to rise and tell

00:26:13.499 --> 00:26:18.259
us where it is obstructed accordingly we do
the exercise.

00:26:18.259 --> 00:26:24.370
Supposing you have a trouble on your head
and you do the stomach exercises, the stomach

00:26:24.370 --> 00:26:26.759
will be spoilt for nothing at all.

00:26:26.759 --> 00:26:31.389
As it is you have a headache plus the stomach
is also spoilt.

00:26:31.389 --> 00:26:34.609
So it is a big science one has to understand.

00:26:34.609 --> 00:26:37.110
But it is so simple as a child.

00:26:37.110 --> 00:26:46.850
Now this child is a realized soul he knows
because you become the absolute.

00:26:46.850 --> 00:26:54.590
Now if you want to know whether there is God
or not you just put your hands like this and

00:26:54.590 --> 00:26:57.570
ask the question, "Mother is there God?"

00:26:57.570 --> 00:27:03.639
When you ask the question you'll get tremendous
Cool Breeze flowing.

00:27:03.639 --> 00:27:07.080
Is like a computer, an absolute computer.

00:27:07.080 --> 00:27:11.899
Now you ask a question, "Was Christ the son
of God?"

00:27:11.899 --> 00:27:17.889
You get tremendous; but ask about Rasputin
"Was he a saint?"

00:27:17.889 --> 00:27:26.789
I don't want to ask because it might burn
My hand.

00:27:26.789 --> 00:27:32.399
That's how you know the absolute.

00:27:32.399 --> 00:27:38.639
Afterwards you don't need also to use the
hands, just without that you know and that

00:27:38.639 --> 00:27:45.850
is what the state one has to achieve, that
is the final break-through we have to achieve

00:27:45.850 --> 00:27:55.590
because this modern times as they say, these
are the times that are described as the resurrection

00:27:55.590 --> 00:28:06.279
time, the judgment time and this is the time
that people have to judge themselves.

00:28:06.279 --> 00:28:09.210
Your own Spirit will judge you.

00:28:09.210 --> 00:28:15.350
Nobody is going to put you on a weighing machine
to see what have you got.

00:28:15.350 --> 00:28:18.989
Your own centers will be judged by you yourself.

00:28:18.989 --> 00:28:24.659
You become your own master, your own Guru
and you judge yourself and correct it.

00:28:24.659 --> 00:28:26.799
You judge others and correct it.

00:28:26.799 --> 00:28:34.919
But you don't tell them, you speak in a strange
language as the disciples of Christ spoke.

00:28:34.919 --> 00:28:36.890
You talk in the language of centers.

00:28:36.890 --> 00:28:39.890
Like you ask somebody, "What's the matter
with this person?"

00:28:39.890 --> 00:28:44.309
So he'll say, "His left Vishuddhi is catching."

00:28:44.309 --> 00:28:46.519
Means he feels guilty.

00:28:46.519 --> 00:28:51.100
If you feel guilty your left Vishuddhi catches.

00:28:51.100 --> 00:28:57.229
We went to Nottingham today and there was
a taxi fellow who came in.

00:28:57.229 --> 00:29:04.869
We sat in the car and I knew he was a realized
soul.

00:29:04.869 --> 00:29:06.120
And he started talking to Me.

00:29:06.120 --> 00:29:16.859
He also took to Me easily and he confessed
to Me, "Mother I am a healer."

00:29:16.859 --> 00:29:20.433
I knew he was a, everybody knew that he was
a realized soul.

00:29:20.433 --> 00:29:24.149
He did not know much about it because he's
not a Sahaja Yogi to know all the deftness

00:29:24.149 --> 00:29:25.149
of it.

00:29:25.149 --> 00:29:31.859
But he knew that he was something different
and a very gentle and a sweet personality

00:29:31.859 --> 00:29:33.100
he had.

00:29:33.100 --> 00:29:34.385
And while talking I asked him, "What's the
matter with you?

00:29:34.385 --> 00:29:35.385
Why do you feel so guilty?"

00:29:35.385 --> 00:29:38.860
He said, "I don't know but I feel like a criminal."

00:29:38.860 --> 00:29:41.529
I said, "Why?"

00:29:41.529 --> 00:29:43.929
"Because everybody thinks I am queer."

00:29:43.929 --> 00:29:52.049
I said, "In a lunatic asylum if a saint man
goes everybody thinks that he is insane.

00:29:52.049 --> 00:29:56.720
So you must not feel that way, you should
have all full confidence in yourself."

00:29:56.720 --> 00:30:00.509
But he was so surprised that I could tell
all these things about him.

00:30:00.509 --> 00:30:05.559
I said, "Anybody would say because we know
what you feel on your finger tips.

00:30:05.559 --> 00:30:09.029
It's nothing great that we are doing."

00:30:09.029 --> 00:30:13.289
Because supposing, dog cannot talk to us,
but supposing we tell the dog that this is

00:30:13.289 --> 00:30:15.090
music, Indian music.

00:30:15.090 --> 00:30:21.720
He will ask, "How do you know it is Indian
music?"

00:30:21.720 --> 00:30:22.721
Because we know, we can hear.

00:30:22.721 --> 00:30:26.230
You can't hear; you cannot differentiate.

00:30:26.230 --> 00:30:31.280
But we don't take such pride in saying that
we know this color or we know that thing and

00:30:31.280 --> 00:30:33.570
we know what is art, what is not.

00:30:33.570 --> 00:30:38.049
We think it is our own right to know and we
know it.

00:30:38.049 --> 00:30:44.470
In the same way once you get your Realization
you just know it because you become.

00:30:44.470 --> 00:30:55.509
So becoming is the main thing that you become
a realized soul, a saint, a sage, a seer,

00:30:55.509 --> 00:31:02.700
but as a result of this awakening because
it passes through various centers, into various

00:31:02.700 --> 00:31:03.700
layers.

00:31:03.700 --> 00:31:10.350
First thing that happens to you; first thing
I must say that you get your physical body

00:31:10.350 --> 00:31:11.350
cured.

00:31:11.350 --> 00:31:16.649
That's how Sahaja Yoga cures cancer.

00:31:16.649 --> 00:31:19.019
What is so great about it?

00:31:19.019 --> 00:31:24.470
It does and it's only this Sahaja Yoga that
is going to cure cancer.

00:31:24.470 --> 00:31:28.580
Otherwise you'll take chemotherapy, loose
your hair, then they'll cut your throat and

00:31:28.580 --> 00:31:36.419
cut your nose and you'll end up by parts,
you see and when one will die it won't be

00:31:36.419 --> 00:31:37.710
in one piece.

00:31:37.710 --> 00:31:44.669
But in Sahaja Yoga the Kundalini rises and
she supplies the necessary vital forces to

00:31:44.669 --> 00:31:50.340
all these centers and you get cured.

00:31:50.340 --> 00:31:58.099
Practically everything that is to be repaired
can be repaired if the stage is not very much

00:31:58.099 --> 00:31:59.099
advanced.

00:31:59.099 --> 00:32:05.289
If the stage is very much advanced then the
Divine takes a decision that let this body

00:32:05.289 --> 00:32:09.669
die and come back again in a fresher way.

00:32:09.669 --> 00:32:14.779
Then it allows it to die.

00:32:14.779 --> 00:32:22.190
But mostly if it is in a repairing stage without
taking any medicine, without going to any

00:32:22.190 --> 00:32:27.769
doctor, without anything you can cure yourself.

00:32:27.769 --> 00:32:31.840
It's not difficult.

00:32:31.840 --> 00:32:38.080
It transforms your personality in the sense
that your priorities change completely.

00:32:38.080 --> 00:32:40.179
I don't have to tell you 'don't do this'.

00:32:40.179 --> 00:32:43.159
That I will not say because then half of you
may run away.

00:32:43.159 --> 00:32:53.879
But it will happen in such a manner that you
yourself won't do that.

00:32:53.879 --> 00:32:55.249
I don't have to tell you at all.

00:32:55.249 --> 00:33:03.249
Because firstly if you try to do it you will
lose your vibrations you feel unhappy.

00:33:03.249 --> 00:33:13.210
You'll lose your joy and peace and maybe your
body may react and that it may vomit out the

00:33:13.210 --> 00:33:24.739
thing or it may make you very painful so that
you just don't do it.

00:33:24.739 --> 00:33:27.129
You become righteousness, you become virtuous
and you enjoy your virtues.

00:33:27.129 --> 00:33:31.499
You don't force your virtues on others you
just say that one day he should get Realization.

00:33:31.499 --> 00:33:43.970
The concern is as if a part of your body is
sick and you want to soothe it and put it

00:33:43.970 --> 00:33:44.970
right.

00:33:44.970 --> 00:33:45.970
No obligation, nothing.

00:33:45.970 --> 00:33:54.220
If somebody is drowning himself actually part
of you is getting drowned that's why you jump

00:33:54.220 --> 00:33:55.529
into it.

00:33:55.529 --> 00:34:04.059
But here actually you feel the another person
and if you know how to cure that then there's

00:34:04.059 --> 00:34:07.409
no obligation at all because there is a part
and parcel of your being.

00:34:07.409 --> 00:34:08.409
Supposing this finger is paining and if I
rub it.

00:34:08.409 --> 00:34:10.050
Am I obliging myself?

00:34:10.050 --> 00:34:17.419
But it is so spontaneous it is so automatic
that the idea also doesn't come into your

00:34:17.419 --> 00:34:19.560
head that you have obliged him.

00:34:19.560 --> 00:34:22.530
It's so simple.

00:34:22.530 --> 00:34:26.260
This is the power of God's love.

00:34:26.260 --> 00:34:28.610
We have never used that before because we
were not capable of doing that.

00:34:28.610 --> 00:34:35.110
All these wars and all these problems of the
world are because we are using the power of

00:34:35.110 --> 00:34:36.110
hatred.

00:34:36.110 --> 00:34:44.770
We talk of peace but how will you make peace
on this earth when the people are so disturbed?

00:34:44.770 --> 00:34:54.590
The source of peace is the Spirit and if the
whole world or a part of it and a very wee

00:34:54.590 --> 00:35:03.360
part of it accepts that they should have their
Spirit manifesting and they establish themselves

00:35:03.360 --> 00:35:04.360
you'll see all these problems will vanish
into thin air.

00:35:04.360 --> 00:35:08.380
As it is in your private life they vanish
out.

00:35:08.380 --> 00:35:11.310
Everything becomes smooth joyous happy.

00:35:11.310 --> 00:35:29.280
The relationships become very pure and you
really enjoy human beings for the first time.

00:35:29.280 --> 00:35:32.170
Otherwise it is just we'll say "Oh we are
brothers, brothers, brothers.

00:35:32.170 --> 00:35:34.080
We are sisters, we are this that."

00:35:34.080 --> 00:35:41.720
When it comes to selfishness everything drops
out because it's just a mental projection.

00:35:41.720 --> 00:35:46.170
Even countries will say we are all friends,
we are going to help, but when it comes to

00:35:46.170 --> 00:35:47.780
something important they drop out.

00:35:47.780 --> 00:35:50.350
But this is no mental projection, is reality.

00:35:50.350 --> 00:36:02.210
Become that and that should happen to many,
many people by that a kind of a catalysism

00:36:02.210 --> 00:36:08.000
will take place and the whole world has to
be changed as promised.

00:36:08.000 --> 00:36:16.240
Those days are ahead, is working out very
well, I have worked in this England for ten

00:36:16.240 --> 00:36:17.240
years.

00:36:17.240 --> 00:36:27.920
In India hardly two years, but thousands and
thousands in the villages are now Sahaja Yogis.

00:36:27.920 --> 00:36:29.471
They have given up all their bad habits.

00:36:29.471 --> 00:36:32.920
They have become masters of themselves.

00:36:32.920 --> 00:36:38.580
Even I would say in England we have quite
a lot of Sahaja Yogis, but still is a very

00:36:38.580 --> 00:36:45.650
important place is England because it plays
a very important role in spirituality because

00:36:45.650 --> 00:36:54.460
it is the heart of the universe and the heart
