00:38:00.840 --> 00:38:03.130
Today I had a very, very hectic day.

00:38:03.130 --> 00:38:13.340
The whole day I have been moving from places
to places and somehow you have been so kind

00:38:13.340 --> 00:38:19.380
to come here and I am sure we'll get the experience
tonight.

00:38:19.380 --> 00:38:26.170
But in any case if you have any questions
please ask.

00:38:26.170 --> 00:38:30.310
Is important.

00:38:30.310 --> 00:38:43.070
From the seekers: May I ask a question Mataji?

00:38:43.070 --> 00:38:47.620
Mother: Yes please.

00:38:47.620 --> 00:38:54.200
From the seekers: Is it possible to awaken
Kundalini without a spring guidance like You

00:38:54.200 --> 00:38:57.400
because You are not available to us so only
by reading books?

00:38:57.400 --> 00:38:58.400
Mother: Yes it is possible.

00:38:58.400 --> 00:38:59.400
Only

00:38:59.400 --> 00:39:00.400
Sahaja Yogi: 'Only by reading books' she said

00:39:00.400 --> 00:39:01.400
Mother: By reading books.

00:39:01.400 --> 00:39:02.400
No, no, no not at all.

00:39:02.400 --> 00:39:03.400
Kabir Das has said "Padhi, padhi pandita murakha
bhayei".

00:39:03.400 --> 00:39:04.700
That by reading too much even the learned
have become stupid.

00:39:04.700 --> 00:39:11.480
Seeker: So how could we have Divine guidance
like You?

00:39:11.480 --> 00:39:17.470
Mother: What you have to do first of all is
to know that it's a living process and for

00:39:17.470 --> 00:39:21.330
any living process you don't need mental understanding.

00:39:21.330 --> 00:39:28.870
Just I have talked to you because after all
you are very intelligent people.

00:39:28.870 --> 00:39:33.680
But supposing we want to sprout a seed what
do we do?

00:39:33.680 --> 00:39:38.980
We put it in the Mother Earth and it sprouts.

00:39:38.980 --> 00:39:42.540
Do we give it a lecture before hand?

00:39:42.540 --> 00:39:47.870
All right do we do anything?

00:39:47.870 --> 00:39:53.530
It is built-in in the seed as well as in the
Mother Earth the capacity to do it.

00:39:53.530 --> 00:40:00.821
So of course you have to have somebody who
has the capacity.

00:40:00.821 --> 00:40:01.821
Satguru is the real Guru.

00:40:01.821 --> 00:40:04.250
But these days they are all in the market;
all making money.

00:40:04.250 --> 00:40:10.440
First thing is no money can be paid for sprouting
of the seed; first principle.

00:40:10.440 --> 00:40:21.610
Ninety nine point nine percent [99.9%] will
drop out on that point and is said that 'Sahib

00:40:21.610 --> 00:40:22.610
Milaye'.

00:40:22.610 --> 00:40:28.480
The one who makes you meet the Divine is the
Guru.

00:40:28.480 --> 00:40:30.850
The one who talks and gives lecture is not
the Guru.

00:40:30.850 --> 00:40:38.410
But these days there are some very great Gurus
but they are hiding themselves in the Himalayas

00:40:38.410 --> 00:40:43.760
and I sent one of them with great request
to America that please go and do some work

00:40:43.760 --> 00:40:45.790
in America I won't be able to go.

00:40:45.790 --> 00:40:49.380
He stayed in New York for three days and ran
back into Himalayas.

00:40:49.380 --> 00:40:54.860
He said, "The people are at a very lower level
you see, they just talk of dollar."

00:40:54.860 --> 00:40:57.320
He ran away.

00:40:57.320 --> 00:41:05.450
So they don't want to deal just now perhaps
maybe after sometime if they see that the

00:41:05.450 --> 00:41:06.770
area is all right, they may come down.

00:41:06.770 --> 00:41:11.780
But there are many great saints all over the
world.

00:41:11.780 --> 00:41:14.370
But sort of they have receded themselves.

00:41:14.370 --> 00:41:24.980
First you all become saints and they will
all come to join.

00:41:24.980 --> 00:41:30.900
Seeker: To become saint is very difficult.

00:41:30.900 --> 00:41:33.570
Mother: Who told you that?

00:41:33.570 --> 00:41:34.570
Seeker: Afreed

00:41:34.570 --> 00:41:35.570
Mother: It is the easiest thing.

00:41:35.570 --> 00:41:36.700
Living process is the easiest.

00:41:36.700 --> 00:41:40.610
But we are so difficult we don't want to eat
like this we want to go round and eat, then

00:41:40.610 --> 00:41:43.270
say...It is the simplest thing.

00:41:43.270 --> 00:41:48.730
'Sahaja Samadhi Lago', Sahaja you get it.

00:41:48.730 --> 00:41:54.960
Is said by everyone who said it is difficult?

00:41:54.960 --> 00:41:58.440
Who has said it tell me?

00:41:58.440 --> 00:41:59.600
No one.

00:41:59.600 --> 00:42:04.250
'Ek hi akshar premaka pade so pandita ho'.

00:42:04.250 --> 00:42:06.570
Who has said it?

00:42:06.570 --> 00:42:08.900
Did Christ say so?

00:42:08.900 --> 00:42:11.220
Did Buddha say so?

00:42:11.220 --> 00:42:12.220
Nobody said.

00:42:12.220 --> 00:42:19.630
But they could not do it because people were
difficult.

00:42:19.630 --> 00:42:27.510
So they said all right go ahead, carry on.

00:42:27.510 --> 00:42:33.590
Krishna at the very outset of Gita he said
that you find yourself.

00:42:33.590 --> 00:42:37.500
You become a 'sthita pragya'.

00:42:37.500 --> 00:42:40.000
You become a realized soul, at the very outset.

00:42:40.000 --> 00:42:46.830
But Arjuna says, "But how You are telling
me to go on war and here You are telling me

00:42:46.830 --> 00:42:48.650
to become 'saakshi', the witness?"

00:42:48.650 --> 00:42:51.500
Krishna was a Father.

00:42:51.500 --> 00:42:57.550
He said, 'This gentleman won't understand
in a straight way.'

00:42:57.550 --> 00:43:02.980
Because Krishna is a special incarnation of
diplomacy, he understand how human beings

00:43:02.980 --> 00:43:04.190
are, like a Father you see.

00:43:04.190 --> 00:43:05.200
He won't tell straight forward.

00:43:05.200 --> 00:43:08.880
He will say 'all right you want to do it go
ahead.'

00:43:08.880 --> 00:43:12.190
You want to jump in the sea go ahead.

00:43:12.190 --> 00:43:19.550
So He said, "All right," it's very interesting
we don't understand Gita also without Realization.

00:43:19.550 --> 00:43:26.890
Like a father who comes out of his house and
sees his son trying to drive the cart.

00:43:26.890 --> 00:43:32.750
So he says, "All right you want to drive the
cart please put the horse before the cart."

00:43:32.750 --> 00:43:38.740
But the son says, "No I can put the horse
behind and drive the cart."

00:43:38.740 --> 00:43:42.500
He said, "All right do it no harm.

00:43:42.500 --> 00:43:44.210
Only put your attention there."

00:43:44.210 --> 00:43:49.190
So he says that, "All right you do all your
work, but put it at the Lotus Feet of the

00:43:49.190 --> 00:43:50.190
God."

00:43:50.190 --> 00:43:53.900
You cannot do it, is an absurd condition.

